cdata.name: Bankera
cdata.desc: Bankera is building a regulated bank for the blockchain era, which means that it will be a digital bank with traditional banking services and will support both cryptocurrencies and fiat currencies. Bankera wants to reduce the dependency on the counterparties to the minimum and be a core participant of the financial markets. Bankera already has a minimum viable product (MVP) via SpectroCoin.com.
